{# Reads runtime signals discovered in select-signal phase #}
{# For each signal, checks: frequency vs baseline, pattern signatures,
  defense-layer firing, regulation action triggered, action distribution shift #}
{# Emits `cns.runtime.classify` span per classified threat (P9) #}
{# Applies pragmatic-cybernetics: trace signal polarity (increasing/decreasing risk?),
  variety of signal sources (alternative indicators for same threat?),
  Good Regulator check (is defense layer regulating the threat?) #}
{# Every finding requires concrete evidence: span target, timestamp,
